This directory contains a meta model for RDFS and OWL ontologies.
Use the java class i5.cb.ontology.OntologyTransformer
to transform an existing ontology to a set of Telos
files. These files can then be told to a ConceptBase server,
if the meta model has been loaded before.

01_rdfs.sml
    Contains the basic definitions for objects from the RDFS
    model.

02_rdfs-rules.sml
    Some rules and constraints to simplify the handling of RDF_List

03_owl.sml
    The definitions for concepts of the OWL model.

04_owl-gts.sml
    Graphical Types for the OWL model, to enable a nice
    browsing and editing of OWL ontologies in the CB GraphEditor

05_owl-queries.sml
    Some queries for ontologies, used by the special ontology
    components in the GraphEditor


    